HEADWORD: Glass-crab
<hw>Glass"-crab`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The larval state (<spn>Phyllosoma</spn>) of the genus
<stageof><gen>Palinurus</gen></stageof> and allied genera. It is
remarkable for its strange outlines, thinness, and transparency. See
<er>Phyllosoma</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>glasscutter</ent>⟦br⟧
